title: Looking for duo friend to get out of silver
body:
Hi, I am looking for a serious player looking to get out of silver. I am an ex Gold player that got placed in silver. Its really hard to climb solo cause of some Bronze players that lack some ingame knowledge. I main Jungle, ADC and I am decent with a few champions in others lanes. I main Elise, Jinx,Nocturne, Urgot,Kindred. 
My ingame name is Kevjordan add me up
